  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 19.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PHONE RINGING] Into work-- they were-- they were-- they were called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[CLEARS THROAT] And my father was taken into the work, work battalion.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "That was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was like in February 1942.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, anyway, my father was taken in by the Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was taken into the-- not into a work battalion, what's called [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "All the Jewish men were taken into, into those work battalions.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They were-- they had a yellow armband on their, on their, on their sleeves.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they would do mostly work, all kinds of work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then he was shipped out to the Ukraine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I understand most of those work battalion people, they were used to clear mines on the front line, to dig trenches, ditches.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They prepared, you know, defensive lines for the, for the, for the Hungarian armies.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I never-- I was never to see his again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The only thing I remember he-- we got a telegram in 1943 that he disappeared.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He disappeared in a town in the Ukraine called [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Buchenei, ?] and I was never to see him again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My mother was left with the six children.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I, being the oldest, you know, I had to provide the best I can, you know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went into a little business.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned how to make bootleg.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I still do, but I wouldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And, and, and we had like, a little [NON-ENGLISH], which is called-- like, you know, where the people would come into drink, and they would pay so much for a drink, you know?",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother, my mother, took care of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was rough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "During the war years, it was very rough.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, in 1942, there was a famine because when the Hungarian army went in-- when, when Hungry went into war, they took away all the food.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everything was taken away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We weren't able to make our own bread anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And once a week they would bring bread, and the bread was rationed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And Jews would even get less rations.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And there was a famine.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There was a famine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember one guy walking into my great grandfather in his house and say, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Give me a piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And as he said it, he fell on the floor, dead.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "People were dying from hunger.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There was just-- didn't-- they didn't-- and I'll tell you something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "When there is a famine, it's psychologically.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That's all you think about is, is food.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "At night, I remember I used to go to sleep-- usually at night, when you sleep, you sleep-- but constantly, you were thinking of food.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Constantly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "This is a-- it's, it's a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "A famine is a terrible thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And that was in 1942.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Very, very bad.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "In 1943, it was a little better because people got used to, they knew how to adjust themselves to this type of life.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And there was more food available.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the war was raging, especially those days, the war was raging away from Hungary.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "It was way, way, way inside the Soviet Union, so we didn't even know there is a war around.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "In the beginning of 1944, my mother said, time has come for me not to stay in the village anymore, but to go into the city, to the big city, which is called Satu Mare, or Sathmar, and I should learn a trade.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I went to, to Satu Mar.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a Hungarian man, his name was [?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maunail Lawyish. ?] And he gave me a job to learn how to be a locksmith.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I learned how to be a locksmith and also to do welding.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maunail Lawyish, ?] by the way, he was the head of the Nyilas Party in Sathmar.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He wasn't the head, but he was a member of the Nyilas.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Nyilas were the Hungarian Nazis, and I worked for them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Of course, when I did something wrong in working, he would hit me, you know?",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because this was the style.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If you learn something, if you didn't understand or something, they would give you a slap in the face.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As I said before, maybe it's not a good method.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't beat because I was Jew, because I was stupid, or something, or I did something ridiculous, so he hit me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But every Friday afternoon, he would say to me in Hungarian, [?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yakup-- ?] because I was called in Hungarian [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yakup-- ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Yakup, ?] it's late Friday, Friday afternoon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Shabbats is coming.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You can't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Go back.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I would always go back Friday afternoon, and I was living there in a, in a, in a children's home there.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And that's it, so I would go home.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
